{"tid":118732,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"［風水野］話時話…大家有冇幫架車拜下神","createTime":"2017-02-13T08:33:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T15:39:02.000Z","uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e2e9db77fd0dfceb6ff77d5a687bf5b8a09ac9b","tid":118732,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T08:33:19.000Z","msg":"話說我細佬買左架二手車返嚟揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都揸左差唔多一年 一路都出入平安算係幾順利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係佢今日同我講 話佢公司有個同事既媽媽（細佬同同事關係幾好 會間唔中同佢同事屋企人食下飯）問佢有冇信教 咁我細佬就話冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住同事媽媽就叫佢拜下神 因為佢見到有個人坐左喺佢架車入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要已經唔係第一次 所以先會同我細佬講聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味 佢而家聽完就有啲淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想問下各位巴絲有冇呢啲習慣？想知道下求個心安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好害我細佬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢生平冇乜做過壞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/13/163147_f44d14ef198d9fed9dd668182f93e256.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F13%2F163147_f44d14ef198d9fed9dd668182f93e256.jpg&h=a370e9fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6c55827df4be46e7644e1539fee97f75e3b35b2","tid":118732,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a76ed21c0548afbc064386bc1dc481f15b55c16","tid":118732,"uid":5806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:12:21.000Z","msg":"佢朋友老母有幻覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7e4dec7b836667c35fc73cc093b739140e36fe","tid":118732,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:15:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ce89d309117c8b32d8a238bc2af206d33b85e0b","tid":118732,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:37:55.000Z","msg":"咁有冇人買架車返嚟真係會拜下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3b6c806d540438371605297ba82d153fe00841","tid":118732,"uid":19715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:55:31.000Z","msg":"坐係車到個個就係你細佬loo"},{"pid":"218ad74707986aa99342cecf2e785607110f1aa7","tid":118732,"uid":30929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T15:39:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢老母想同你性交轉運咋</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}